00:30:59.030 --> 00:31:00.330
selalu kabur.

00:31:01.920 --> 00:31:02.940
Setiap saat?

00:31:07.790 --> 00:31:08.460
Ya.

00:31:10.200 --> 00:31:11.330
Aku punya mimpi yang sama

00:31:12.790 --> 00:31:14.420
